[
  {
    "startTime": 0.0,
    "endTime": 3.18,
    "text": "It's a super populated manga and anime"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 3.18,
    "endTime": 6.12,
    "text": "character in Japan, whose name is"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 6.12,
    "endTime": 7.720000000000001,
    "text": "Detective Conan."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 8.252,
    "endTime": 9.622,
    "text": "There he is, that's real."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 9.75,
    "endTime": 13.11,
    "text": "Detective Conan, yes..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 13.11,
    "endTime": 16.61,
    "text": "Detective Conan..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 16.716,
    "endTime": 18.666,
    "text": "Ladies and gentlemen, Detective Conan is"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.666,
    "endTime": 21.746000000000002,
    "text": "a man who's trapped in a child's body"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.746,
    "endTime": 23.875999999999998,
    "text": "and solves crimes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 24.666,
    "endTime": 27.641000000000002,
    "text": "Sound a little familiar?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.368,
    "endTime": 28.668,
    "text": "I don't solve crimes,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 28.668,
    "endTime": 31.288,
    "text": "but I'm a man trapped in a child's body,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.288,
    "endTime": 32.708,
    "text": "my name is Conan."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.708,
    "endTime": 35.418,
    "text": "Now I have established that Detective Conan is clearly"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.488,
    "endTime": 38.228,
    "text": "a rip-off of yours truly."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.228,
    "endTime": 40.868,
    "text": "Detective Conan was created in 1994,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.868,
    "endTime": 44.623000000000005,
    "text": "that's year after I went on the air"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.623,
    "endTime": 47.293,
    "text": "to instant international acclaim."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.213,
    "endTime": 53.417,
    "text": "Now, get this, Detective Conan is so popular in Japan"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.817,
    "endTime": 60.187,
    "text": "that there is an actual city Hokuei that's been renamed Conan Town."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.202,
    "endTime": 61.802,
    "text": "I'm not making this up."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 61.802,
    "endTime": 63.732,
    "text": "A whole city called Conan Town."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 63.732,
    "endTime": 66.522,
    "text": "Get this, Conan Town even named their"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.522,
    "endTime": 70.25200000000001,
    "text": "train station and their air port after Detective Conan."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.373,
    "endTime": 72.973,
    "text": "Now, clearly, you have to be a genius to see"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.873,
    "endTime": 76.165,
    "text": "someone's making a lot of money off the Conan name."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.969,
    "endTime": 79.119,
    "text": "Wouldn't you agree, Andy the attorney?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.484,
    "endTime": 81.574,
    "text": "Absolutely, it's an open-and-shut case."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.574,
    "endTime": 83.604,
    "text": "Thank you very much."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.554,
    "endTime": 85.864,
    "text": "Thank you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.135,
    "endTime": 90.095,
    "text": "I'd ask you but you didn't go to any graduate school."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.285,
    "endTime": 94.155,
    "text": "I...I've..I haven't been listening."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.376,
    "endTime": 97.936,
    "text": "Finally, I've got a sidekick that listens to me,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.966,
    "endTime": 99.401,
    "text": "and he's only here for one night."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 99.436,
    "endTime": 106.016,
    "text": "Anyway, so the other night, I reasonably asked Japan to pay me 3 trillion yen,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.42,
    "endTime": 108.256,
    "text": "because I thought that was only fair."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.256,
    "endTime": 109.706,
    "text": "This thing has made a lot of money"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 109.706,
    "endTime": 111.836,
    "text": "for a long time for 24 years."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 111.836,
    "endTime": 114.076,
    "text": "Plus, I asked the mayor of Conan Town to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 114.076,
    "endTime": 118.086,
    "text": "change the name of the town's most popular coin laundry to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.154,
    "endTime": 120.204,
    "text": "American Conan's FLUFF 'N FOLD,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 120.204,
    "endTime": 122.344,
    "text": "which I thought was fair. -[Andy] small price"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.344,
    "endTime": 124.47399999999999,
    "text": "Small price. And I asked them to change"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 124.474,
    "endTime": 126.854,
    "text": "the hair on their Detective Conan statue"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 126.854,
    "endTime": 130.884,
    "text": "to something a little more iconic and recognizable around the world."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 133.951,
    "endTime": 135.831,
    "text": "Well..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 137.512,
    "endTime": 139.272,
    "text": "the plot thickens."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 139.272,
    "endTime": 141.87199999999999,
    "text": "Over the weekend, the mayor of Conan Town"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141.872,
    "endTime": 146.692,
    "text": "responded to my very reasonable request with his own set of demands."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 146.642,
    "endTime": 148.84199999999998,
    "text": "He made a video. Let's take a look."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 149.382,
    "endTime": 151.512,
    "text": "Hello from Hokuei Town,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 151.512,
    "endTime": 155.512,
    "text": "aka Conan town in Japan."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 155.512,
    "endTime": 158.482,
    "text": "I am Mayor Matsumoto."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 158.482,
    "endTime": 162.482,
    "text": "I have a few modest demands too."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 162.486,
    "endTime": 163.576,
    "text": "First:"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 163.576,
    "endTime": 165.356,
    "text": "I want my face next to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 165.356,
    "endTime": 167.05599999999998,
    "text": "President Lincoln"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 167.056,
    "endTime": 170.936,
    "text": "on Mout Rushmore."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 170.936,
    "endTime": 172.466,
    "text": "Second:"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 172.466,
    "endTime": 174.126,
    "text": "I want my own star"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 174.126,
    "endTime": 177.326,
    "text": "on the Hollywood Walk of Fame"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 179.372,
    "endTime": 181.58200000000002,
    "text": "Finally:"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 181.582,
    "endTime": 183.962,
    "text": "I want you to bring"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 183.962,
    "endTime": 186.482,
    "text": "15,000"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 186.482,
    "endTime": 188.912,
    "text": "American hamburgers"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 188.912,
    "endTime": 191.752,
    "text": "with you when you come."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 192.88,
    "endTime": 196.88,
    "text": "That's one for each citizen of Conan Town."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 199.021,
    "endTime": 200.21099999999998,
    "text": "Be here..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 200.211,
    "endTime": 202.33100000000002,
    "text": "or be square."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 211.372,
    "endTime": 213.942,
    "text": "Don't mess with that guy!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 213.942,
    "endTime": 218.132,
    "text": "Clearly, I did not realize who I was dealing with."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 218.222,
    "endTime": 220.21200000000002,
    "text": "Mayor Matsumoto, I know you're watching,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 220.212,
    "endTime": 222.232,
    "text": "and I say this with all respect,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 222.232,
    "endTime": 224.242,
    "text": "you are a very shrewd negotiator."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 224.242,
    "endTime": 225.322,
    "text": "You got me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 225.322,
    "endTime": 229.342,
    "text": "I will fulfill all three of your request."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 229.342,
    "endTime": 232.40200000000002,
    "text": "You wanted your face out at the Mount Rushmore,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 232.382,
    "endTime": 233.872,
    "text": "but I'll do you one better,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 233.872,
    "endTime": 236.67200000000003,
    "text": "instead of sharing Rushmore with four other people,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 236.652,
    "endTime": 238.12199999999999,
    "text": "who wants that?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 238.122,
    "endTime": 243.012,
    "text": "I got you your very own mountain right here in Burbank California."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 242.982,
    "endTime": 244.612,
    "text": "Check it out!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 247.289,
    "endTime": 250.539,
    "text": "(audience cheering) - [Andy]wow"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 250.539,
    "endTime": 251.909,
    "text": "Look at that!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 251.909,
    "endTime": 254.469,
    "text": "He is emerging from the hillside."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 254.738,
    "endTime": 256.388,
    "text": "Isn't that amazing?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 256.388,
    "endTime": 257.58799999999997,
    "text": "[Andy] Yeah"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 257.627,
    "endTime": 259.767,
    "text": "Now trust me, trust me Mayor,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 259.767,
    "endTime": 265.167,
    "text": "this is an actual real window looking out on an real mountain,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 265.257,
    "endTime": 266.157,
    "text": "isn't that right, Andy?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 266.157,
    "endTime": 267.447,
    "text": "It's Burbank alright,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 267.447,
    "endTime": 269.467,
    "text": "cause I can keep an eye on my wife."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 269.467,
    "endTime": 270.877,
    "text": "Alright, very nice."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 271.628,
    "endTime": 274.108,
    "text": "What do you say other Andy? Real right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 274.108,
    "endTime": 275.318,
    "text": "Absolutely real."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 275.318,
    "endTime": 276.64799999999997,
    "text": "Spoken like a true lawyer."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 276.648,
    "endTime": 282.708,
    "text": "Next, you asked me for a star on the Hollywood Walk of Fame."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 282.728,
    "endTime": 285.385,
    "text": "Luckily for you, I'm a pretty big deal in this town,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 285.455,
    "endTime": 287.155,
    "text": "and in show business in general,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 287.155,
    "endTime": 290.85499999999996,
    "text": "I made one of two phone calls and went right to the top,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 532.2,
    "endTime": 534.589,
    "text": "and I easily got you your star on the Hollywood Walk of Fame."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 534.589,
    "endTime": 535.7600000000001,
    "text": "Take a look."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 535.76,
    "endTime": 544.17,
    "text": "(audience laughing and clapping)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 544.17,
    "endTime": 554.03,
    "text": "(Conan laughing like a maniac)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 554.03,
    "endTime": 560.769,
    "text": "And finally, you asked for"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 560.769,
    "endTime": 569.03,
    "text": "150,000 American hamburgers,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 569.03,
    "endTime": 571.579,
    "text": "one for every resident in Conan Town."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 571.579,
    "endTime": 579.1999999999999,
    "text": "The problem is, Mr. Mayor,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 579.2,
    "endTime": 582.2900000000001,
    "text": "I don't know how everybody likes them,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 582.29,
    "endTime": 587.05,
    "text": "some people like theirs medium rare,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 587.05,
    "endTime": 591.12,
    "text": "some like them well done,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 591.12,
    "endTime": 599.839,
    "text": "so I'm gonna (drum) ...so..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 599.839,
    "endTime": 606.36,
    "text": "a little early..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 606.36,
    "endTime": 609.86,
    "text": "(Conan and audience laughing)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 609.86,
    "endTime": 618.8100000000001,
    "text": "So..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 618.81,
    "endTime": 624.27,
    "text": "so I'm gonna ship you all the material"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 624.27,
    "endTime": 630.18,
    "text": "you need to make the burgers yourselves!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 630.18,
    "endTime": 634.9899999999999,
    "text": "Yes!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 634.99,
    "endTime": 647.1,
    "text": "(audience cheering)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 647.1,
    "endTime": 646.1800000000001,
    "text": "That's right, Mr. Mayor, that's right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 646.18,
    "endTime": 652.3389999999999,
    "text": "In one week's time,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 652.339,
    "endTime": 660.149,
    "text": "in exactly one week's time,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 660.149,
    "endTime": 664.589,
    "text": "this steer will be parachuted into Conan Town,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 664.589,
    "endTime": 673.11,
    "text": "for you and your citizens can do whatever you like to have"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 673.11,
    "endTime": 675.0600000000001,
    "text": "perfect American hamburgers."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 675.06,
    "endTime": 680.6999999999999,
    "text": "Let's get this shipping label"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 675.06,
    "endTime": 680.6999999999999,
    "text": "on that steer right now!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 680.7,
    "endTime": 685.73,
    "text": "Let's get it ready to go!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 685.73,
    "endTime": 693.72,
    "text": "Yes!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 693.72,
    "endTime": 696.4200000000001,
    "text": "(audience cheering)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 696.42,
    "endTime": 703.2099999999999,
    "text": "Very nice."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 703.21,
    "endTime": 707.48,
    "text": "Mayor Matsumoto, I met all of your demands."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 707.48,
    "endTime": 712.64,
    "text": "Now it's time for me to call your bluff."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 712.64,
    "endTime": 717.6999999999999,
    "text": "I want my 3 trillion yen,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 717.7,
    "endTime": 724.4200000000001,
    "text": "so here's what's gonna happen,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 724.42,
    "endTime": 730.389,
    "text": "and this is real,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 730.389,
    "endTime": 734.1800000000001,
    "text": "next week I am flying to Japan and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 734.18,
    "endTime": 739.9399999999999,
    "text": "coming to Conan Town to collect my money."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 739.94,
    "endTime": 747.3800000000001,
    "text": "I'll be there!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 747.38,
    "endTime": 752.02,
    "text": "I'm going to be there!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 752.02,
    "endTime": 756.9499999999999,
    "text": "And Mr. Mayor, I'lll be square!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 756.95,
    "endTime": 760.9100000000001,
    "text": "(audience cheering)"
  }
]